data.description: ASK US ABOUT THE ASSUMABLE LOAN:  UNDER 3%! Single story Pool home in TURN-KEY condition on a cul-de-sac.  This beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home with 2588 sq ft of open living space boasts hardwood floors and tile throughout living room, dining room and kitchen areas. The kitchen has a large center island with bar seating, granite counters, stainless appliances, double oven, large breakfast nook with built in bench seating and plenty of cabinet space. The living room/Dining room flows into a family room with fireplace, media center and surround sound.  The large primary bedroom has views of the backyard, spacious en suite bathroom with tiled shower, dual sinks, soak tub, and an oversized walk in closet. 3 additional bedrooms with a guest bathroom with dual sinks as well as a powder room off of the living space. An indoor laundry room with cabinets and folding space too.  The A/C condenser was replaced in 2023 as well.  Enjoy your private backyard with a pebbletec pool that is automated with water features and LED lighting, outdoor kitchen with TV, traeger smoker and built in bbq.  A gated side area is great for your dogs if you have them!  A large driveway and 3 car, side-by-side garage with plenty of storage.  Even the front yard provides a lovely porch with sitting area. Assumable Loan information: Buyer will have to qualify and bring in the difference, but the seller has a very low interest rate on the loan and it is able to be assumed for a fee.
